Take a look to [Block helpers handlebars][1], in your case you can create a helper to change the name variable like this: 

.hbs

    &lt;div class=&quot;entry&quot;&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;{{title}}&lt;/h1&gt;
     &lt;div class=&quot;name&quot;&gt;
      {{#nameHelper}}{{name}}{{/nameHelper}}
     &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

script.js

    Handlebars.registerHelper(&#39;nameHelper&#39;, function(options) {
    return new Handlebars.SafeString(
      &#39;&lt;div class=&quot;name&quot;&gt;&#39;
      + options.fn(otherName)
      + &#39;&lt;/div&gt;&#39;);
    });


  [1]: https://handlebarsjs.com/block_helpers.html

